---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TravelList from '../components/TravelList.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Underrated Atlas" description="An evolving list of underrated places — originally crowd-sourced from Farcaster in 2023 and added to since.">
  <article>
    <h1>Underrated Atlas</h1>
    <p>As of 2023, I've visited 47 countries. My hope is to make it to 100 before I kick the bucket.</p>
    <p>One thing that becomes obvious the more you travel: it's usually not the capital cities or postcard panoramas that teach you the most about a region. Most major cities and tourist meccas start to blur together.</p>
    <p>It's the places further out that show you how local people actually live, eat, shop, work, and learn.</p>
    <p>They're the most likely to feel magical.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">The list below was originally compiled from the Farcaster community in 2023, and I've added to it since with recs from travel-aficionado friends.</p>
    <TravelList />
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
